            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, bash your <strong>hazelnuts</strong> in their bag with a <strong>rolling pin</strong> (keep them in the bag so you don't lose any!)</p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Combine <strong>half</strong> your <strong>cider vinegar</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) with a drizzle of<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><strong>olive oil</strong> in a bowl with a pinch of <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your<strong> dressing</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1678467919100-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
