            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1678468267886-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1678468267886-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> mushroom & red wine glazed sausage risotto</strong> with the <strong>dressed salad </strong>to the side</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>toasted hazelnuts</strong>, <strong>remaining thyme leaves</strong> and a generous crack of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
